claim: Black Panther did not appear in mainstream American comics.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is the first black superhero in mainstream American comics , debuting years before such early African-American superheroes as Marvel Comics ' the Falcon  (  1969  )  and Luke Cage  (  1972  )  , and DC Comics ' Green Lantern John Stewart  (  1971  )  and Black Lightning  (  1977  )  .
